programme.title: 大法官 THE JUDGE
programme.desc: An established city lawyer reconnects with his estranged family when he returns home to help defend his father who is suspected of murder. 事业有成的大城市律师回到家乡帮助涉嫌杀人的爸爸证明清白，同时和分离已久的家人重建情谊。.(n)

programme.title: 动物方城市 ZOOTOPIA
programme.desc: A rabbit police officer partners a red fox con artist to uncover a conspiracy involving the disappearance of savage predator inhabitants of a mammalian metropolis. 免子刑警茱蒂与狐狸骗徒连手揭发「动物方程市」市内，猎食动物莫名失踪背后所隐藏的阴谋。.(n)

programme.title: 第22条军规 CATCH-22 S1 06
programme.desc: Alive and intact, Yossarian is thwarted by an old adversary. Confronted by a devastating loss, he undergoes a transformation. 尤塞恩毫发无伤的活着，并受到一名宿敌的阻挠。他遭受惨痛的损失，并经历一场转变。.(n)

programme.title: 离婚S3:02 DIVORCE S3 02: MIAMI
programme.desc: Robert admits to pre-wedding jitters as Frances prepares for a weekend getaway with Henry. 《离婚》第三季回归，这出由莎拉洁西卡帕克与哈登邱奇领衔主演的辛辣喜剧，描写长期婚姻生活所面临的困境。.(n)

programme.title: 温特的故事:泳不放弃2 DOLPHIN TALE 2
programme.desc: The team at Clearwater Marine Hospital needs to find a new companion for Winter the dolphin soon before it is forced to move to another aquarium. 海洋医院的团队必须在海豚温特被迫转到别间水族馆之前，帮牠找到新的同伴。.(n)

programme.title: 阿达一族 THE ADDAMS FAMILY
programme.desc: Con artists plan to fleece the eccentric family using an accomplice who claims to be Uncle Fester. 阿达一族的大家长高魔子带着一家子人住在一栋阴森森的维多利亚式宅院中，高魔子心中唯一挂念的就是已经离散25年的哥哥….(n)

programme.title: 黑客任务完结篇：最后战役 THE MATRIX REVOLUTIONS
programme.desc: Neo, Trinity, and Morpheus lead the final battle for humankind's survival. 在这部划时代科幻三部曲的完结篇中，邪恶的机器大军无情地进攻锡安，由莫斐斯领军的志愿军深知，这场战役要获胜最终还是要靠尼欧。.(n)

programme.title: 购物狂的异想世界 CONFESSIONS OF A SHOPAHOLIC
programme.desc: A shopaholic lands a job as a financial journalist to support her addiction, but her compulsive shopping habits and growing debts threaten to derail her career. 血拼成瘾的丽贝卡负债累累，她必须想办法维持收入的稳定，勉强窝在财经杂志做记者的她是否会重回过去毫无节制的购物狂生活？.(n)

programme.title: 第一千金欧游记 CHASING LIBERTY
programme.desc: While on a diplomatic trip to Europe with her parents, first daughter Anna escapes the secret service and meets mysterious stranger Ben Calder. 总统千金庭曼蒂摩儿躲过特勤人员的监视，在欧洲享受单人旅程。.(n)

programme.title: 布偶奇遇记 FRAGGLE ROCK S3 04: BLANKET OF SNOW, BLANKET OF WOE
programme.desc: Mokey forgets to cover Marjory the Trash Heap during a heavy snow and the Fraggles’ beloved oracle freezes solid. 玛吉忘了在大雪之时用毯子遮盖堆肥婆婆，结果这个大家钟爱的智者竟被冻结了。.(n)

programme.title: 布偶奇遇记 FRAGGLE ROCK S3 05: PEBBLE POX BLUES
programme.desc: Boober risks terrible dangers in order to get to the Cave of Shadows, where he can gather the medicinal plants needed by his sick friends. 布伯冒着极大的危险前往黑暗洞穴帮生病的好友采集药材。.(n)

programme.title: 汉克大冒险 HANK ZIPZER S3 03: ZIPZERS AND ALIENS
programme.desc: Hank accidentally gets his friends’ books confiscated by Miss Adolf and has to put things right before the author herself makes a very special visit to Westbrook. 汉克不小心害好友的书被阿朵芙老师没收，他要如何在书的作者到学校访问之前收拾残局呢？.(n)

programme.title: 汉克大冒险 HANK ZIPZER S3 04: EDUCATING ZIPZER
programme.desc: A film crew is coming to the school and Hank accidentally becomes the central figure in their documentary. 电影制作团队来学校录制纪录片，汉克意外成为他们拍摄的主要目标。.(n)

programme.title: 布偶历险记 THE MUPPETS
programme.desc: Together with his friends, a Muppet fan raises money to help save the Muppet Theater from being part of a nasty plan! 木偶的超级粉丝华特和好友一起想办法筹得挽救木偶剧院所需的一千万元。.(n)

programme.title: 三十姑娘一朵花 13 GOING ON 30
programme.desc: Jennifer Garner sheds her tough girl 'Alias' look to star in the hilarious comedy of a 13-year-old who wakes up one day and discovers that she's 30. 性格古怪的吉娜最大的心愿就是长大成人，从十三岁变成三十岁受欢迎的熟女。某次她碰到一种魔尘，让她一夕之间真的从13岁变成30岁但她很快便发现，长大并不如想象中那么酷….(n)

programme.title: 烘焙屋的怒吼 NO CONTRACT, NO COOKIES: THE STELLA D'ORO STRIKE
programme.desc: A group of workers goes on a strike to protect their livelihood in real life documentary. 这出纪录片透过第一线的访谈揭露纽约布朗克斯市史黛拉迪欧罗饼干工厂的员工为了维持生计及工作状态而展开的战争….(n)

programme.title: 朗福勋爵 LONGFORD
programme.desc: An HBO Original Movie based on the true story of a respected politician who stakes his name and career to campaign for a notorious serial killer. 七世纪的朗佛郡伯爵法兰克，是当代英国史上最受争议的人物。而他与杀人凶手米拉辛德莉的友情，却可能令他的政治生涯面临前所未有的危机，以及造成玉石俱焚的后果。.(n)

programme.title: 出窍情人 JUST LIKE HEAVEN
programme.desc: A couple who live on different sides of the divide of life and death discover the boundaries love can cross in this romantic comic fantasy. 戴维发现前任房客伊丽莎白还没将东西清空，甚至能够随意进出公寓，其实伊丽莎白正躺在医院中陷入昏迷,戴维的迁入让伊丽莎白逐渐了解事情的真相，而他们是否能在所剩无几的时间内让伊丽莎白起死回生呢？.(n)

programme.title: 型男飞行日志 UP IN THE AIR
programme.desc: George Clooney is Ryan Bingham, a corporate downsizing expert whose cherished life on the road is threatened. 一名企业资遣专家及飞行常客莱恩宾罕，在常年过着逍遥自在的生活之后，突然发现他准备敞开心房，和一位女子发展一段感情。.(n)

programme.title: 建国箴言 THE WORDS THAT BUILT AMERICA
programme.desc: This documentary features iconic documents written by America’s founding fathers, which provide a blueprint for America’s democracy. 这出纪录片探讨由美国开国元勋所撰写的独立宣言、美国宪法与美国权利法案，这些重要文献成为美国民主政体的蓝图。.(n)

programme.title: 大小谎言 BIG LITTLE LIES S2 05: KILL ME
programme.desc: Renata attempts to help Celeste; Bonnie relives painful memories of her mother. 第二季剧情描写谎言的恶意蔓延、坚定的友谊、脆弱的婚姻以及完美教养方式下的残忍真相。.(n)

programme.title: 哈里斯太太 MRS. HARRIS
programme.desc: A prep-school headmistress falls for a philandering doctor and causes his death. Was it a murder or an accident? 本片为HBO自制电影中，由安奈特班宁主演。金结识了贺曼塔诺瓦医生二人展开了热烈的爱情，但塔诺瓦医生却不改风流本性，瞒着金到处偷吃...(n)

programme.title: 母子威龙 STOP! OR MY MOM WILL SHOOT
programme.desc: She does his laundry, irons his clothes and cooks his dinner. Now Sylvester Stallone’s mom is going to clean up his streets! 动作片巨星席维斯史特龙饰演洛城警署的硬汉警佐乔波莫斯基，他这次终于遇上了毕生最难缠的对手：他的老妈。当乔的妈妈进城来看他时，却因缘际会地成为一宗杀人案的目击证人….(n)

programme.title: 乌龙元首 HEAD OF STATE
programme.desc: Chris Rock stars in this hilarious political comedy, as he finds himself plucked from obscurity and running for President of the United States! 快嘴喜剧演员克里斯洛克在这部讽刺时局的喜剧中自导自演，大开美国选举制度的玩笑。.(n)

programme.title: 推倒白宫的男人 MARK FELT: THE MAN WHO BROUGHT DOWN THE WHITE HOUSE
programme.desc: Based on a true story of the most famous anonymous man in American history, Mark Felt, who was the "Deep Throat" whistleblower in the 1970s WaterGate scandal. 本片改编自真实事件，剧情描述美国史上最知名的匿名男子：马克费尔特，也是1970年代水门案丑闻的”深喉咙”的故事。.(n)

programme.title: 昆汀塔伦提诺之恶夜追杀令 FROM DUSK TILL DAWN
programme.desc: Two criminals and their hostages unknowingly seek refuge in a club that is inhabited by vampires. 乔治克鲁尼和昆丁泰伦提诺饰演两个兄弟逃犯，一个聪明灵巧，令一个失控凶狠。他们找了一家子当作人质，接着横越墨西哥边界来到脱衣舞吧，却不知遇到一群饥饿的吸血鬼。.(n)

programme.title: ANGEL HOME
programme.desc: ANGEL HOME tells the story of Mako, a woman who lives in a group home with her father because her mental development stopped at a kindergarten level.(n)

programme.title: HERO (2002)
programme.desc: Jet Li stars in this visually arresting martial arts epic as an unnamed fighter who claims to have battled the three most dangerous assassins out to kill the king.(n)

programme.title: INTIMATE ENEMIES
programme.desc: Four people find a large sum of money illegally belonging to a conglomerate president and decide to use it to take revenge on corrupt corporations.(n)

programme.title: MAKE A BOW AND KISS
programme.desc: Graduating president of her high school archery club An Kishimoto must pass on the reins to Mikami Yota, a junior who possesses a secret love for her.(n)

programme.title: 走进走出 The Family Court - EP 13
programme.desc: (R) Shu Ya accuses Le Shan of framing her in court but he denies her claim, saying that it is the client who misunderstood his intention. (重)舒雅质问乐山为什么要陷害她？乐山矢口否认，狡辩说自己只是好心给秀秀提供一些有关离婚的法律知识，是秀秀误解了他的意思，舒雅感失望。众人都觉得乐山已经变了，变得急功近利，没有人性，舒雅说乐山早就违背了当初想做一个好律师的理念。.(n)

programme.title: 甘味人生 Taste Of Life - EP 172
programme.desc: Zhao Ju Cai and his wife Li Jin Xiu have five children. Devoted all his life to developing soy sauce products, much as Zhao Ju Cai hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father's pursuit of invention, the Zhao brothers' lives are about to change. (PG)赵居财，一生致力研发酱油产品，与妻李锦琇育有五个孩子；居财虽然希望众孩子之中有人接手经營家业，但也尊重孩子们的兴趣和志向。赵家兄弟也因为父亲赵居财的「发明梦」，人生逐渐起了变化。.(n)

programme.title: 西瓜甜不甜 Say Cheese - EP 5
programme.desc: (R) It's National Day and Xi Gua Shu accidentally loses his tickets to the National Day Parade. His tickets are found by Liu Lian Sao. Overjoyed, she brings Yuan Hang and her neighbours to watch the parade. Before leaving for the show, she learns that Xi Gua Shu had lost his tickets and realises she had picked up his tickets. However, she does not return them to him. She only tells him after the show, thus angering Xi Gua Shu. (PG)(重)国庆日，西瓜叔不小心掉了国庆演出的票，被榴梿嫂捡了去，高兴地和远航以及邻居一起去看。临行前，她听说西瓜叔掉了门票的事，恍然自己捡到的门票是西瓜叔的，但却不肯把票还给他，而是看了演出之后才故意对西瓜叔说自己的门票是捡来的，气坏了西瓜叔。.(n)

programme.title: 老友万岁 Old Is Gold - EP 31
programme.desc: Jun Yang is elated when Shu Mei regains consciousness, but the doctor says that Shu Mei will be partially paralysed. It would affect her ability to move about, and even to talk. Jun Yang wants to postpone the wedding until Shu Mei's health is better. Silver does not agree, and suggests that Jun Yang should send Shu Mei to a nursing home, but Jun Yang is determined not to do so. (PG)俊阳欣喜淑梅终于苏醒，但医生却无奈告知淑梅半身瘫痪，以后不止行动不便，就连说话都会很吃力。俊阳希望将婚礼延后，等淑梅情况好转后再办。但Silver不同意，暗示俊阳应该把淑梅送进疗养院，俊阳坚决不肯。.(n)

programme.title: 周公找茶 Dennis Uncovers - EP 4
programme.desc: When Dennis - our well-known Radio DJ cum comedian - invites his celebrity friends over for "kopi", expect a no-holds-barred conversation. As the caffeine takes effect, Dennis works on uncovering secrets from his guests. His guest celebrities are not just restricted to famous personalities in show-business, they include among others successful people from the world of sports, arts and fashion. Set in a cafe where cameras are almost not in sight, recording starts the moment Dennis steps in. 十年磨一剑，好歌喉靠父母栽培；与音乐导师周杰伦擦出哪些火花？.(n)

programme.title: 流氓经纪2 My Agent Is A Hero S2 - EP 4
programme.desc: Bert found Ah Hua and Ah Gui betting at the gambling den and was exasperated. Ah Gui felt guilty for gambling again and even stealing his wife's money to gamble. On the other hand, Tiger finally arrives in Singapore and expected to meet Bert, but Bert got caught up in a last-minute issue. (PG)Bert在赌档发现阿花和阿鬼竟然都在赌钱，气急败坏。二人输了很多钱，后来Bert和赌档老板赌，借此拖延时间，等待佳叔报警来捉人。警察捉人之后，Bert怒骂阿鬼，之前不是戒赌了？阿鬼哭着说自己又赌钱了，还偷了老婆的钱。 另一方面，Tiger终于来到新加坡了，要和Bert见面。Bert本来打扮好好要去见面的，没想到临时碰到问题。.(n)

programme.title: 一切从昏睡开始 While You Were Away - EP 12
programme.desc: Sen Mei and Guan Ming meets a client who pressures them to drink. Xia Luo Ke sends the photos of them drinking to Zi Jun and Zi Jun's face darkens. He decides to wait for her downstairs and sees Guan Ming sending Sen Mei home. Zi Jun brings Sen Mei back home, both parties blame one another and starts an argument. Zi Jun accuses Sen Mei of having an affair with Guang Ming and Sen Mei is taken aback. (PG)森美与冠铭见客户，为应酬而不得已喝酒。夏洛克将两人喝酒的照片传给子骏，子骏脸色一沉，到楼下等待，果然见到冠铭送森美回来。子骏带森美回家，夫妻俩互相指责，最后吵起来。子骏脱口说出森美与冠铭有染之事，森美感错愕！.(n)

programme.title: Athlétisme - Meeting d'Eugene
programme.desc: Une saison enfin lancée. Eloigné des pistes pendant plusieurs semaines, Renaud Lavillenie fait son grand retour à Stanford pour la nouvelle étape de la Diamond League. Opposé au champion olympique brésilien Thiago Braz, au champion du monde américain Sam Kendricks et au champion d'Europe suédois Mondo Duplantis, le recordman du monde de la discipline devra réaliser des sauts de classes mondiales pour s'imposer dans l'un des moments phares de ce meeting Californien.(n)

programme.title: Athlétisme - Athletissima
programme.desc: De retour à son top niveau. Après avoir donné naissance à un petit Zyon en 2017, Shelly-Ann Fraser fait de nouveau trembler le sprint mondial. Dans un meeting de Lausanne relevée avec la Britannique Dina Asher-Smith et l'Ivoirienne Marie-José Ta Lou, la double championne olympique et triple championne du monde du 100 m voudra de nouveau faire parler la poudre pour s'imposer dans cette nouvelle manche de la Diamond League.(n)

programme.title: Champions Weekly
programme.desc: Alors que la saison a pris fin sur le sacre du FC Liverpool, le magazine consacré à la Ligue des champions propose un numéro spécial pour revenir sur l'ensemble de l'exercice, depuis la phase de groupes qui a débuté en septembre 2018 jusqu'à la finale disputée à Madrid le 1er juin dernier.(n)

programme.title: Champions League : le flop du PSG
programme.desc: Les années se suivent et se ressemblent. Incapable de se hisser en quart de finale de Ligue des champions, depuis plusieurs saisons, le PSG a une nouvelle fois failli dans les grands rendez-vous européen. Des résultats de prestige face à Liverpool et Naples jusqu'au fiasco face à Manchester United, RMC Sport revient sur le nouveau flop du club de la capitale dans la plus prestigieuse des compétitions européennes.(n)

programme.title: Buzzer été

programme.title: Athlétisme - Meeting de Marseille
programme.desc: Un plateau de choix. Pour la 13ème édition du meeting de Marseille, les plus grandes stars françaises et internationales ont répondu à l'appel. Jimmy Vicaut sur 100m, Rénelle Lamotte, la double vice-championne d'Europe sur 800m mais surtout la nouvelle sensation américaine du 400m haies, Sydney McLaughlin devraient briller lors de cette deuxième étape du Pro Athlé Tour.(n)

programme.title: Basket-ball - France / Turquie
programme.desc: Les choses sérieuses commencent enfin pour les Bleues. Après avoir brillé sans forcer, deux fois, face à l'Ukraine, l'équipe de France féminine de basket vont pouvoir se jauger plus sérieusement à quelques jours du grand début de l'Euro. Face à une solide formation de Turquie, les Françaises pourront se reposer sur la vista de Marine Johannès pour continuer à faire le plein de confiance.(n)
